ChunkGenerator - Class in me.desertfox.dgen.chunk
The ChunkGenerator class manages the process of generating rooms
and other objects into a shard

If you made a new ChunkGenerator subclass then don't forget to register it ChunkGenerator.register(Class)
Otherwise it won't be accessible

Keep in mind every instance of your class will represent a shard
